## Data Collection

Data was collected manually from personal purchase records including email receipts, bank statements, and wear-tracking logs. Each row represents one item with the following fields:

`date` · `brand` · `item_name` · `category` · `color_family` · `price_paid` · `times_worn` · `still_own` · `purchased_where` · `season` · `notes`

---

Built as part of my data analyst portfolio to demonstrate end-to-end data storytelling from raw collection through to a presentation.
